{"tid":176580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港被納入粵港澳大灣區","createTime":"2017-03-28T09:21:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-28T11:34:52.000Z","uid":3017,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"77eeb700c67c958ef19bd8c41c09207e37fefa49","tid":176580,"uid":3017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T09:21:34.000Z","msg":"總理在今年的《政府工作報告》正式把「粵港澳大灣區」納入其中，這意味著，包括深圳在內的珠三角核心區的11個城市將迎來巨大的發展機遇，而更是有專家預測深圳將會成為「灣區大哥」！<br />\n<br />\n全力打造全球第四大灣區<br />\n<br />\n「粵港澳大灣區」主要包括深圳、香港、澳門、廣州、東莞、珠海、佛山、中山、惠州、江門、肇慶<br />\n<br />\n國際一流灣區有紐約灣區、舊金山灣區和東京灣區。經濟高度發達！粵港澳大灣區的GDP總量已經達到1.24萬億美元，超過了舊金山灣區，未來的目標就是成為第四大灣區！灣區的建設將全面提升區內城市的地位和價值，深圳將邁向世界級城市！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2ef4ce5237fd291c8f5fb11532f7ca380fd375b","tid":176580,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T09:26:21.000Z","msg":"So what?香港人咪又係......"},{"pid":"e6bb975062b530c730a999c2d5850637d098a978","tid":176580,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T09:27:04.000Z","msg":"借機會吸乾香港發展深圳 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9603f58aabf6c78378aa39b042b9b14d84164c6a","tid":176580,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T09:30:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>借機會吸乾香港發展深圳 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n慢慢消失於世界<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冇咁快，十年左右啦。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;深圳&ldquo;，就包括埋大家宜家身處的香港。"},{"pid":"750be07a1db6fc13fe7a812ab68fbe96c56aa4a8","tid":176580,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T09:31:52.000Z","msg":"粵港澳湛周生生我就識"},{"pid":"02c86b0f065afeb08be267e9d75e77c7bda48ec8","tid":176580,"u